  Mem Alerts

  This option allows you to select the type of alert when the pager
  is in silent (MEM-O-LERT) mode.

        Vibrate         - Pager will vibrate for 12 seconds
        Chirp & Vibrate - Pager will chirp once and vibrate for 12 seconds
        None            - Pager will neither chirp nor vibrate.

        NOTE: In each case, the LED will flash.
